msgctxt "announce_finesthour"
msgid "The long wait is almost over! The <c(f5d167)>COMMONWEALTH</c> is coming!\n\nA few words from the Prime Minister, Mr. Churchill:\n\nWhat General Weygand called the Battle of France is over. I expect that the Battle of Britain is about to begin. The whole fury and might of the enemy must very soon be turned on us.\n\n Let us therefore brace ourselves to our duties, and so bear ourselves that if the British Empire and its Commonwealth last for a thousand years, men will still say, <c(f5d167)>'THIS WAS THEIR FINEST HOUR'</c>."
msgstr ""

